###

### CREATE MODEL
POST http://{{host}}/api/models
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ruch po okręgu",
  "description": "Model parametryczny 2D",
  "xExpression": "cos(t)",
  "yExpression": "sin(t)"
}

###

### CREATE SIMULATION
POST http://{{host}}/api/simulations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Symulacja bez warunków początkowych",
  "startTime": 0.0,
  "endTime": 10.0,
  "stepSize": 0.1,
  "status": "CREATED",
  "dynamicModelId": 1
}

###

### ADD INITIAL CONDITION TO SIMULATION
POST http://{{host}}/api/simulations/2/initial-condition
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "x0": 1.0,
  "y0": 0.0
}

###

### GET INITIAL CONDITION FOR SIMULATION
GET http://{{host}}/api/simulations/2/initial-condition
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### UPDATE INITIAL CONDITION FOR SIMULATION
PUT http://{{host}}/api/simulations/2/initial-condition
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "x0": 2.0,
  "y0": 1.0
}

###

### GET SIMULATION BY ID
GET http://{{host}}/api/simulations/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### DELETE INITIAL CONDITION FOR SIMULATION
DELETE http://{{host}}/api/simulations/2/initial-condition
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET ALL SIMULATIONS
GET http://{{host}}/api/simulations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET MY SIMULATIONS
GET http://{{host}}/api/simulations/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

